Paulina (paulina@ai.mit.edu) will take people who want to relax and have a good time XC skiing in pretty civilized conditions very near home. Probably at Weston Ski Track (accessible by T in a pinch). Will teach beginners. Half-day on Sunday (morning) with an option to stay later by yourself. <br>
Equipment: XC skis</td>
